# =============================================================================
# Public repository policy: this repo ships ONLY the Python pipeline code
# (src/, tests/, config/, requirements, Makefile, README, licenses).
# Generated data, model-response caches, and the paper's data artifacts are
# NOT tracked here; they ship alongside the paper (../paper/) and/or a data
# archive. The pipeline regenerates everything under data/ and results/ from
# public sources (see README).
# =============================================================================

# Virtual environment
.venv/
venv/

# Python
__pycache__/
*.py[cod]
*.egg-info/
.pytest_cache/
.coverage
htmlcov/

# Generated data, caches, and coded datasets (regenerated by the pipeline;
# the paper-relevant subset ships with ../paper/). Nothing under data/ or
# results/ is tracked in the public code repo.
data/
results/

# Notebook checkpoints
.ipynb_checkpoints/

# Secrets / local env
.env
*.local

# OS / editor noise
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
.vscode/
.idea/

# Local working notes and scratch (not part of the released pipeline)
/PLAN.md
/*.local
*.tmp
